@startuml profile-edit-state
' Context: profile
' SDD: PROM-PROFILE-IDENTITY
' Revision: 2026-07-18

title Profile — ProfileController state machine (own profile)

state Idle : isSaving = false\nisUploadingAvatar = false
state Saving : isSaving = true
state UploadingAvatar : isUploadingAvatar = true

[*] --> Idle

Idle --> Saving : SaveProfile
Saving --> Idle : ProfileSaved
Saving --> Idle : ProfileSaveFailed\n[error set]

Idle --> UploadingAvatar : UploadAvatar
UploadingAvatar --> Saving : upload ok\n+ SaveProfile(avatarUrl)
UploadingAvatar --> Idle : AvatarUploadFailed\n[error set]

note right of Saving
  ProfileScreen chiama
  AuthController.refreshProfile()
  dopo save riuscito
end note

@enduml
